Name: Speed
Description:
Granting the character the ability to move faster and react faster
The method is manually activated by the keys [A, D]

Attribute.Name: speed
Attribute.Description: Enables the character to move faster, granting the ability to react faster

Name: Gravity
Description:
Granting the character the ability to jump higher and reach higher places
The method is manually activated by the key [W]

Attribute.Name: gravity
Attribute.Description: Enables the character to jump higher, granting the ability to reach higher places

Name: MultipleJumps
Description:
Granting the character the ability to jump multiple times before landing and reach further places
The method is manually activated by the key [W]

Attribute.Name: multipleJumps
Attribute.Description: Enables the character to jump multiple times before landing, granting the ability to reach further places

Name: FireballShoot
Description:
Granting the character the ability to shoot fireballs and destory special obstacles
The method is manually activated by the key [Q]

Attribute.Name: fireballShoot
Attribute.Description: Enables the character to shoot fireballs, granting the ability to destory special obstacles

Name: InverseGravity
Description:
Granting the character the ability to inverse the gravity and turn the game upside down
The method is automatically activated

Attribute.Name: inverseGravity
Attribute.Description: Enables the character to inverse the gravity, granting the ability turn the game upside down

Name: WallJump
Description:
Granting the character the ability to jump and slide from special walls
The method is manually activated by the key [W, A, D]

Attribute.Name: wallJump
Attribute.Description: Enables the character to jump and slide from special walls, granting the ability to parkour

Name: Grabbing
Description:
Granting the character the ability to grab objects and move them
The method is manually activated by the key [E]

Attribute.Name: grabbing
Attribute.Description: Enables the character to grab objects, granting the ability to move objects
